Most Popular Stations Properties¶

So, we have discovered that some stations have more connections than others. Question is, do the stations that connect to the most popular share a feature? And what makes these stations more popular than others?

Findings¶

These initial visualisations show us 3 things:

  • Most popular stations are in Jersey City and near Bergen Square.
  • The number of bikes leaving and arriving per station do not vary much (especially for most popular).
  • Bike destinations are determined by proximity.
